Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:54.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}光も闇もないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}表も裏でも君だよ
